# Fake News Detection Using BERT

This repo contains a BERT-based fake news classifier.

## Setup
1. Download dataset from [Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/clmentbisaillon/fake-and-real-news-dataset).
2. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`.
3. Run: `python fake_news_detector.py`.

## Usage
- Trains and evaluates the model.
- Use `predict(text)` for inference.

Trained on ~45k articles; achieves ~90%+ accuracy.w